Looking for professional painters in the London area and Middlesex County?
 
Dartelle Interior has you covered! From the start of every project to the completion, we go above and beyond when working with our clients to ensure they are fully satisfied with our work.

We take care of everything for our clients, so they can relax. 
Our services go beyond just applying the coats of paint on the wall. 
Our professionals will prepare the wall before painting by filling holes, sanding and removing excess material. 
After preparing the wall, we add the required coating of paint (using high quality products only) to provide a perfect finish.

Relationships are everything to us. As a company, we aim for perfection every time! 
All of our projects are subject to the approval of Dartelle Interior management and are closely monitored.

Our Promise
We strive to exceed our client’s expectations on every project. We do this by using high-end products and by only using high-end painters with knowledge and experience in the industry. Our professionals use a systematic approach for every project to ensure our clients (commercial and residential) are completely satisfied.
